<title type="html"><![CDATA[6/10 (Thu) 5 Wedding Traditions in Taiwan／ Wedding Party Roles (Host: Louie)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=505&amp;p=527#p527"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">Place: Zoom Meeting<br />Agenda:<br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks <br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation</span><br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">Let's join the Zoom meeting this Thursday at 07:00 pm<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pwd=bkR5TEwwZDlpZnBmR0ZzQ2NKSU5MQT09#success">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw ... 09#success</a><!-- m --></span><br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233</span><br /><br />Session 1: 5 Wedding Traditions in Taiwan<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://international.thenewslens.com/article/72100">https://international.thenewslens.com/article/72100</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C_Uf3Xol4RM">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C_Uf3Xol4RM</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Weddings are occasions that always bring people joy. Weddings of different cultures can be very different from one another. Does this article describe your wedding experience? What else customs did you follow in your wedding? If you are still single, would you like to follow these customs? Why?<br />2.Despite the pleasant atmosphere on the wedding day, the preparation and the practice of a wedding can be very exhausting. What is the most impressive memory of your wedding experience? If you are still single, which is the most important part for you?<br />3.What was the regret in your wedding? If you could have again your wedding, what would you do to correct it?<br />4.Do you think the wedding ceremony (and banquet) planning is important? Would you budget and hire a professional planner?<br /><br />Session 2: Traditional Wedding Party Roles and Responsibilities <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.brides.com/wedding-party-roles-4845435">https://www.brides.com/wedding-party-roles-4845435</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Are you a believer in any religion? If yes, how did that affect your wedding? If you are still single, how would you like to design your wedding?<br />2.Have you ever participated in any different kind of or exotic wedding? How does that feel?<br />3.Would you like to make your wedding whimsical? Or rather traditional and decent? Why?<br />4.Do you think the emcee （司儀）is important in a wedding party? Would you budget to hire an emcee for your wedding party?<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">P.S.<br />1.因疫情關係，聚會方式改為線上遠距。<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~</span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Thu Jun 03, 2021 11:41 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
